          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/58012641-men-in-the-sun">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4064676959" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16197286850637833322">Words...<br/><br/>Words from Palestine. <br/><br/>Words...not like those news that you have been reading in print, electronic &amp; social media since who knows when.<br/><br/>Words...like you have never read before. <br/><br/>Words...that choke you, make you gasp for breath, force you to fathom what its like to be under the scorching heat of injustice, oppression. <br/><br/>Words...that awaken your existence...make you shudder and realize how fortunate you are and those who aren&apos;t fortunate enough to live in this cruel world. <br/><br/>Words...that leave yo</span>
  <span id="freeText16197286850637833322" style="display:none">Words...<br /><br />Words from Palestine. <br /><br />Words...not like those news that you have been reading in print, electronic &amp; social media since who knows when.<br /><br />Words...like you have never read before. <br /><br />Words...that choke you, make you gasp for breath, force you to fathom what its like to be under the scorching heat of injustice, oppression. <br /><br />Words...that awaken your existence...make you shudder and realize how fortunate you are and those who aren't fortunate enough to live in this cruel world. <br /><br />Words...that leave you speechless.<br /><br />Ghassan Kanafani...I bow. <br /><br />Must read in every inch of sense.</span>
